casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Kenneth Conway WYANT, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157070
COA: 339450 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 30, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the January 3, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
